    <string name="repo_list_info_title">Bhanđárò ki List</string>
    <string name="repo_list_info_text">Ek bhanđár, apps ka source hota hai. Is list mè is waqt joŕe hue sabhi bhanđárè dikháye gaye haì. Disable kiye hue bhanđárò ka istemál nahì kiya jata hai.
\n
\nAgar koyi app, ek se zyáda bhanđár mè ho, list mè únce pad par maujúd bhanđár ko apne áp preference diya jata hai. Áp long press aur drag karke bhanđárò ka kram badal sakte haì.</string>
